title: Round 1 Game 1 NBA Reactions
description:
Israel Gutierrez, Domonique Foxworth and Spencer Hall debate how they see the rest of the Nets-Celtics series playing out and if their expectations for Anthony Edwards and the T-Wolves have changed.
